  • Package starvationevasion.common

    • Class starvationevasion.common.Policy extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • owner

          EnumRegion owner
          Every policy card must have an owner. This is the player region from who's deck the card was drawn. Note all automatic policy cards are enacted by the owner and only the owner (enactingRegionBits is ignored).

        • approvedRegionBits

          int approvedRegionBits
          This is a bitwise int with a 1 in the position corresponding to each region that has approved the policy (EnumRegion.getBit()).
          Note: This field is ignored for all automatic policy cards.
          Note: The player who owns a policy always has an automatic approve vote. and does not actually get to submit a vote.

        • targetFood

          EnumFood targetFood
          This field is ignored if this policy does not require a target food.

        • targetRegion

          EnumRegion targetRegion
          Some cards require the target region to be a US player region. Other cards require the target region to be a non-player world region. This field is ignored if this policy does not require a target region.

        • varX

          int varX
          Some policy cards require quantity X, Y and/or Z. The units of these values are depend on the particular policy. The field is ignored if this policy does not require that field.

        • varY

          int varY
          Some policy cards require quantity X, Y and/or Z. The units of these values are depend on the particular policy. The field is ignored if this policy does not require that field.

        • varZ

          int varZ
          Some policy cards require quantity X, Y and/or Z. The units of these values are depend on the particular policy. The field is ignored if this policy does not require that field.
